      Sunspire Health - Heartland
    

                  Sunspire Health Heartland is a treatment facility in Gilman, Illinois offering individualized, patient-centered care for adult men and women suffering with addiction and co-occurring mental health disorders. Heartland is located on 33 acres of sprawling farmland about two hours south of Chicago.
              

